he united states air force battleswars vietnam war awards defense distinguished service medal  air force distinguished service medal  army distinguished service medal navy distinguished service medal coast guard distinguished service medal defense superior service medal legion of merit  distinguished flying cross  meritorious service medal  air medal  french legion of honor jumper speaking as a ceo of leidos september  john p jumper born february   is a retired united states air force general who served as th chief of staff of the united states air force from september   to september   he retired from the air force on november   jumper was succeeded as chief of staff by general t michael moseley contents  background  education  assignments  television  flight information  awards and decorations  effective dates of promotion  tanker lease scandal  thunderbirds thundervision scandal  notes  external links backgroundedit jumper was born in paris texas he earned his commission as a distinguished graduate of virginia military institutes air force rotc program in  he has commanded a fighter squadron two fighter wings a numbered air force and us air forces in europe and allied air forces central europe prior to becoming chief of staff of the air force the general served as commander of air combat command at langley air force base jumper has also served at the pentagon as deputy chief of staff for air and space operations as the senior military assistant to two secretaries of defense and as special assistant to the chief of staff for roles and missions a command pilot with more than  flying hours principally in fighter aircraft jumper served two tours in southeast asia accumulating more than  combat hours jumper retired from the air force on november   in june  jumper joined board of directors of science applications international corporation a federal contractor company on march   jumper become saics ceo and was essential in splitting the company into two after the split jumper remained the ceo of the company which changed its name to leidos jumper retired as ceo in july  when roger krone succeeded him as the companys new ceo but jumper stayed on as chairman of the companys board of directors educationedit  hampton high school hampton virginia  bachelor of science degree in electrical engineering virginia military institute lexington  squadron officer school maxwell afb alabama  air command and staff college maxwell afb alabama  master of business administration degree golden gate university san francisco california  national war college fort lesley j mcnair washington dc assignmentsedit june  – july  student pilot th pilot training squadron moody air force base georgia july  – september  c upgrade training sewart afb tennessee october  – october  c pilot th tactical airlift squadron phu cat air base south vietnam november  – july  f upgrade training st tactical fighter squadron george afb california july  – may  instructor pilot weapons officer and fast forward air controller th tactical fighter squadron udon royal thai afb thailand june  – july  instructor pilot flight examiner and standardization and evaluation chief st tactical fighter wing royal air force bentwaters england july  – august  flight instructor later flight commander us air force fighter weapons school nellis air force base nevada august  – june  student air command and staff college maxwell air force base alabama june  – august  staff officer for operations and readiness tactical division headquarters us air force washington dc august  – july  student national war college fort lesley j mcnair washington dc july  – february  chief of safety th tactical fighter wing nellis afb nevada march  – july  commander th tactical fighter squadron nellis afb nevada july  – august  special assistant and executive officer to the commander headquarters tactical air command langley afb virginia august  – february  vice commander later commander rd tactical fighter wing eglin air force base florida february  – may  commander th fighter weapons wing nellis afb nevada june  – april  deputy director for politicomilitary affairs strategic plans and policy directorate the joint staff washington dc may  – february  senior military assistant to the secretary of defense washington dc february  – july  special assistant to the air force chief of staff for roles and missions washington dc august  – june  commander th air force and us central command air forces shaw air force base south carolina june  – november  deputy chief of staff for air and space operations headquarters us air force washington dc december  – february  commander us air forces in europe and commander allied air forces central europe ramstein ab germany february  – september  commander headquarters acc langley air force base virginia september  – september  chief of staff headquarters us air force washington dc televisionedit jumper appeared as himself in the stargate sg episode lost city part  flight informationedit rating command pilot flight hours more than  aircraft flown c c c c t t f f f fa and eurofighter typhoon awards and decorationsedit command air force pilot badge office of the joint chiefs of staff identification badge office of the secretary of defense identification badge defense distinguished service medal with one bronze oak leaf cluster air force distinguished service medal with one oak leaf cluster army distinguished service medal navy distinguished service medal coast guard distinguished service medal defense superior service medal legion of merit with bronze oak leaf cluster distinguished flying cross with two bronze oak leaf clusters meritorious service medal with two bronze oak leaf clusters air medal with three silver and one bronze oak leaf cluster air medal th consecutive award of this medal denotes second ribbon for accouterment spacing presidential unit citation air force with bronze oak leaf cluster presidential unit citation navy joint meritorious unit award air force outstanding unit award with valor device and two bronze oak leaf clusters air force organizational excellence award with oak leaf cluster combat readiness medal with two bronze oak leaf clusters national defense service medal with two bronze service stars vietnam service medal with silver service star southwest asia service medal with bronze service star global war on terrorism service medal air force overseas short tour service ribbon with bronze oak leaf cluster air force overseas long tour service ribbon with bronze oak leaf cluster air force longevity service award with silver and three bronze oak leaf clusters small arms expert marksmanship ribbon air force training ribbon french legion of honour commandeur medal military meritorious service medal singapore vietnam gallantry cross unit award sicofaa legion of merit officer vietnam campaign medal  air force order of the sword us air forces in europe usafe press release effective dates of promotionedit promotions insignia rank date general november   lieutenant general  september   major general february   brigadier general august   colonel october   lieutenant colonel october   major january   captain june   first lieutenant december   second lieutenant june   tanker lease scandaledit on june   general jumper apologized to senator mccain for internal air force emails about the senator in the context of the tanker lease scandal calling them unprofessional and not worthy of a great air force thunderbirds thundervision scandaledit members of the united states air force were under investigation by the fbi for having awarded a  million contract for audiovisual presentation services to strategic message solutions of plymouth meeting pa the contract involved the thundervision project meant to provide oversized video screens and perhaps content services during air shows that featured the air force thunderbirds the investigation revolves around possible involvement of jumper and then chief of staff of the air force t michael moseley it was suggested that the contract price was inflated because a friend of the two generals air force general ret hal hornburg was associated with strategic message solutions two companies involved in the bidding process protested award of the contract one having offered comparable services for half as much the air force later cancelled the contract notesedit united states air force portal  archived copy archived from the original on  retrieved    httpwwwprnewswirecomnewsreleasessaicannouncesceosuccessionhtml  aitoro jill r  september  what to expect from leidos and saic when they start trading sept  washington business journal retrieved  september    jayakumar amrita  july  leidos taps boeing executive as new ceo washington post retrieved  july    imdb cast listing for episode the lost city part  lists john p jumper playing himself  report faults air force on proposed boeing deal  the san francisco chronicle httpwwwsfgatecomcgibinarticlecgifnanationalwddtl  missing or empty title help  archived copy archived from the original on  retrieved    archived copy archived from the original on  retrieved    archived copy archived from the original on may   retrieved    archived copy archived from the original on  retrieved   external linksedit biography of general jumper usaf september  interview with general jumper air force transformation military aerospace technology may   firstyear cadet criticizes usaf chief of staffs personnel decisions snopes march   speech at the air force association convention september   speech at the air force association symposium february   military offices preceded by gen michael e ryan chief of staff of the united states air force – succeeded by gen t michael moseley v t e chiefs of staff of the air force spaatz vandenberg twining white lemay mcconnell j d ryan brown jones allen gabriel welch dugan loh acting mcpeak fogleman eberhart acting m e ryan jumper moseley mcnabb acting schwartz welsh goldfein authority con